    "description": "<strong>《逐光星火》包含序言与启元星的完整结局，并免费提供2个DLC讲述其他星球的精彩故事，欢迎下载体验！</strong><br><br>官方交流群②：521182604<br>-----------------<br><br><i>“文明的传播可以比作一场大火；首先是微弱的火花，然后是闪烁的火焰，然后是熊熊的烈火，速度和力量都在不断增加。”--尼古拉·特斯拉</i><br><br><br>《逐光星火》是一款科幻叙事游戏。成为来自高等文明的订正者，降临于形态各异的外星世界。引导众生走向繁荣，或将火种扑灭于襁褓之中。通过抉择与策略积蓄力量，突破时空的桎梏前往宇宙中心，决定所有文明的兴衰存亡。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094270/extras/f4468207ecff9efd0854f570c2ee3f54.poster.avif?t=1723625106\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094270/extras/f4468207ecff9efd0854f570c2ee3f54.webm?t=1723625106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094270/extras/f4468207ecff9efd0854f570c2ee3f54.mp4?t=1723625106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >做选择，顺势而为或重塑世界</h2>接触各类外星生命，通过对话了解他们的文化与故事。通过属性能力获取更多的情报，遵循你的感觉做出选择，从改变某位角色的命运到改变整个世界的走向。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094270/extras/5b9179011618d98f621b4acda213f47e.poster.avif?t=1723625106\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094270/extras/5b9179011618d98f621b4acda213f47e.webm?t=1723625106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094270/extras/5b9179011618d98f621b4acda213f47e.mp4?t=1723625106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >观成长，经历构造角色</h2>订正者的成长并不依赖等级或经验，而是取决于你在遭遇中如何抉择。作为一名来自于高等文明的天外来客，你的言行可能比想象中更具影响力。你在游戏世界中的经历和决策，会改变角色属性的强度，最终塑造出一个独属于你的超级生命。<br>《逐光星火》将会为您带来跑团般的沉浸式扮演体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094270/extras/8991ddab4dc94f2c281f3e41eb3da0cb.poster.avif?t=1723625106\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094270/extras/8991ddab4dc94f2c281f3e41eb3da0cb.webm?t=1723625106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094270/extras/8991ddab4dc94f2c281f3e41eb3da0cb.mp4?t=1723625106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建工程，改变未来从改变环境开始</h2>从经营地表上的领地，到建造天体尺度的超级工程，利用订正者强大的技术优势，为其他文明带来繁荣或毁灭。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094270/extras/bef82db98378ae20cf1221dc372d3b61.poster.avif?t=1723625106\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094270/extras/bef82db98378ae20cf1221dc372d3b61.webm?t=1723625106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094270/extras/bef82db98378ae20cf1221dc372d3b61.mp4?t=1723625106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超时空，终结一场遍布全宇宙的漫长战争</h2>跨越时间与空间，寻找聚集众多文明力量的方法。前往宇宙的中心，对抗可以改变物理规律的强大文明，或在黑暗深空中点燃星火和希望。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094270/extras/e5923c317b79824a8b47ee53c480aa69.poster.avif?t=1723625106\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094270/extras/e5923c317b79824a8b47ee53c480aa69.webm?t=1723625106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094270/extras/e5923c317b79824a8b47ee53c480aa69.mp4?t=1723625106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重叙事，可以玩的科幻小说</h2>《逐光星火》以叙事为主，所有的玩法都将为故事服务。希望您能在收获游戏乐趣的同时，也获得阅读科幻小说一样的思辨感。<br>感谢科幻带给我们的勇气、梦想与智慧。",
